ColorectalCancer(x) ::: x is a colorectal cancer.

∀x (SevereCancer(x) → DeadlyDisease(x)) ::: All severe cancers are deadly diseases.

¬(ColorectalCancer(x) ∧ MildFlu(x) ∧ Cholangiocarcinoma(x)) → (BileDuctCancer(x) ∨ Cholangiocarcinoma(x)) ::: If colorectal cancer is not a mild flu and a Cholangiocarcinoma, then colorectal cancer is a bile duct cancer or a Cholangiocarcinoma.
